ui-options-function-ce-toggle-shoot-down-z-level = Toggle aim down (floor)

ce-zlevel-shoot-down-enabled = You aim down through the floor.
ce-zlevel-shoot-down-disabled = You stop aiming down.
ce-zlevel-shoot-down-disabled-unwield = You stop aiming down as your gun is no longer wielded.
ce-zlevel-shoot-down-no-gun = You need to hold a gun to aim down.
ce-zlevel-shoot-down-requires-wield = You need to wield your gun to aim down.
ce-zlevel-shoot-down-no-level = There is no floor below.
ce-zlevel-shoot-up-no-level = There is no floor above.
ce-zlevel-shoot-down-blocked-floor = The floor blocks your shot.
ce-zlevel-shoot-up-blocked-floor = The ceiling blocks your shot.
